column16: Gregg Zaun out on a sacrifice bunt, third baseman Mike Lowell to second baseman Dustin Pedroia.   Aaron Hill to 3rd.    Marco Scutaro to 2nd.
Mark Ellis flies out to center fielder Jacoby Ellsbury.
Travis Buck pops out to second baseman Dustin Pedroia.
Ryan Sweeney grounds out, second baseman Dustin Pedroia to first baseman Kevin Youkilis.
Kurt Suzuki strikes out on a foul tip.
Jack Hannahan homers (1) on a fly ball to right field.    Bobby Crosby scores.
Bobby Crosby singles on a ground ball to center fielder Jacoby Ellsbury.
